project: The objective of this game is to give your pet more food than your opponent.
You do this by playing mini games to collect food.

You click the "Feed" button to feed your pet food. If you did not collect any food during the game, you cannot feed your pet. In the UFO racing game, Planet earth is the finish line. In the falling food game, once your score reaches 20, the game ends and you may feed your pet.
Once your pet reaches 100 in health, you win!
This game is created by Finn Panzer, Elijah Johnson, LJ and Milana Venhrzhenovska
Player 1 uses the key, "W" is used to move forward or jump. The keys, "A" and "D" are used to turn, or to move side to side. The "S" key is used to move backwards.
